Comment: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:50.54,translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}Yet "I want to be with you forever" is the honest truth.
Comment: 0,0:00:51.33,0:00:54.82,translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}Could this feeling be love?
